narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Jessica Head is a Speech-Language Pathologist,   provider based in Denton, TX. From 2024-04 through 2024-12, this provider received $88K in Medicaid payments across 1K claims serving 417 beneficiaries, billing 3 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 95% of all billing comes from a single procedure code: 92507 (92507). This extreme concentration is unusual and may indicate specialized services or a narrow billing pattern.
